{
  "chapter": "022",
  "title": "汉兴以来将相名臣年表",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "太史公序",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝建立以来的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">名臣</span>，已经记载在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>侯表当中了。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：年号\">建元（年号）</span>以来，被封侯的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>则已见于侯表。本表按年次编次<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">名臣</span>的事迹，较为详尽。前代的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>，功勋卓著，为后世所效法，万古流芳。"
    }
  }
}